description:
Storage Hunters, Season 3, Episode 6 or Episode 3.
Title: Behind Closed Doors.

First aired on June 17, 2013.

Description: An unusual auction features two large specialty items. 

Note: there seems to be some mixe-up in the episodes numbering for season 3.  Episode 6 is the original number for the downloaded file but Episode 3 is the most likely right number that I found on the web from its description.  I've also added the title to the original file's name.

It's also possible that's another episode of the end of Season 2 but at this stage, I'm totally lost in the numbers.
